title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Mar 17 2022

description:
OutKick writer Joe Kinsey joins Clay and Buck to discuss biological male swimmer, Lia Thomas, smashing biological female records in NCAA Championship Prelims and predicts good chance will be on the U.S. Olympic women's swim team. Kinsey also talks about the 2022 OutKick Woke All-Star Bracket: "20 Wokes. One Champion." This white man killed by police won’t get George Floyd attention. Elizabeth Warren would flunk high school economics. JetBlue, American and Southwest airline pilots sue the CDC over mandates.
